# 💻 Frontend Examples

## 🧪 Create Topic

```js id="y8e2ru"
await fetch("/teacher/create-topic", {
  method: "POST",
  headers: {
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    Authorization: `Bearer ${token}`
  },
  body: JSON.stringify({
    title: "AI Chatbot",
    description: "NLP assistant",
    status: "draft"
  })
});
```

---

## 🧪 Update Topic

```js id="q1p7sn"
await fetch(`/teacher/update_topic/${topicId}`, {
  method: "PUT",
  headers: {
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    Authorization: `Bearer ${token}`
  },
  body: JSON.stringify({
    title: "Updated Title",
    description: "Updated description",
    status: "published"
  })
});
```

---

## 🧪 Delete Topic

```js id="l4w9zt"
await fetch(`/teacher/delete_topic/${topicId}`, {
  method: "DELETE",
  headers: {
    Authorization: `Bearer ${token}`
  }
});
```

---

## 🧪 Get Draft Topics

```js id="d6m3kv"
await fetch("/teacher/my-drafts", {
  headers: {
    Authorization: `Bearer ${token}`
  }
});
```

